b'Midnight Panther':
b"Based on the Best-Selling Comics From CPM Manga! The traveling musical group The Pussycats is the hottest thing around. Lou, Kei and Sonya are three, sexy singers with a legion of screaming fans in every town. But these pussycats have claws. 

Singers by day, assassins by night. Unbeknownst to their fans, The Pussy Cats are also The Midnight Panthers\xe2\x80\x94female assassins who will kill anyone if the price is right! Their next target is a despotic king who rules by fear and crushes dissension with an iron fist. But for one of the Panthers, it's not just another job... it's personal. 

(Source: AniDB)"
